      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so you won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and honestly feels brand new. Come take a look and see for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
