    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, notch-free shifts, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is structurally flawless with no subframe fatigue, retaining its original suspension geometry and factory-spec damping. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior remains free of typical bolster wear or pixel degradation. A rare, mechanically superlative specimen for the true driving purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
